 <span data-ttu-id="7ccc5-102"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight> 일종의 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.PointLight>위치, 범위 및 감쇠 있기 때문입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ccc5-102"><xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight> is a kind of <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.PointLight>, since it has a position, range, and attenuation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7ccc5-103">그러나 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight> 방향, 모양 및 조명 효과 원뿔의 다른 속성을 제어할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ccc5-103">However, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight> also allows you to control the direction, shape, and other properties of the cone of the light's effect.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ccc5-104">에 대 한 값을 지정할 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight.OuterConeAngle%2A> 는 아무 켜져), (외 및 <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight.InnerConeAngle%2A> 는 모든 항목은 춤) (내 조명 효과 변경 하려면.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ccc5-104">Specify values for <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight.OuterConeAngle%2A> (beyond which nothing is illuminated), and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.SpotLight.InnerConeAngle%2A> (within which everything is fully illuminated) to change the spotlighting effect.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7ccc5-105">외부 원뿔 내부 원뿔 외부 사이의 조명 선형적으로 대체 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7ccc5-105">Lighting between the outside of the inner cone and the outer cone falls off linearly.</span></span>  
  
